SINGLE'S INFERNO

18
00:00:55.722 --> 00:00:56.848
Go-eun!

19
00:01:00.351 --> 00:01:01.186
Yes?

20
00:01:03.563 --> 00:01:04.898
When will you hang out with me?

21
00:01:06.566 --> 00:01:08.109
I'll come down later.

22
00:01:14.365 --> 00:01:15.617
The three of us can hang out.

23
00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:17.202
-Should we do that later?
-Yes.

24
00:01:17.285 --> 00:01:19.746
-We'll come down after we finish talking.
-Okay.

25
00:01:26.503 --> 00:01:29.422
Why can't he just say
he wants to talk with her alone?

26
00:01:29.506 --> 00:01:30.423
-You mean I-geon?
-Yes.

27
00:01:30.507 --> 00:01:33.176
Maybe it's because he knows
Sung-min won't let her go.

28
00:01:33.259 --> 00:01:35.470
-Really?
-Yes. it would make things awkward.

29
00:01:38.223 --> 00:01:41.142
How are you. Mina?
What's going on with you?

30
00:01:41.226 --> 00:01:44.354
As of today. I've made my decision.

31
00:01:44.437 --> 00:01:45.980
-I've decided on one person.
-I see.

32
00:01:46.064 --> 00:01:47.440
After going back and forth?

33
00:01:48.024 --> 00:01:49.692
Yes. I went back and forth a lot.

34
00:01:49.776 --> 00:01:51.820
-A lot?
-Yes. quite a bit.

35
00:01:51.903 --> 00:01:52.987
You must feel relieved.

36
00:01:53.488 --> 00:01:54.864
But he went to Paradise.

37
00:01:55.532 --> 00:01:56.991
-Right.
-Yes.

38
00:01:58.535 --> 00:02:01.621
-I'm off to find my love.
-No. don't go.

39
00:02:01.704 --> 00:02:04.582
-It's Go-eun.
-Yes. I'm off to see Go-eun.

40
00:02:04.666 --> 00:02:07.377
It suddenly occurred to me.
"What am I doing here?"

41
00:02:07.460 --> 00:02:10.588
-Go win her over. Hurry.
-Okay. I will.

42
00:02:13.633 --> 00:02:15.135
Those words are necessary too.

43
00:02:16.052 --> 00:02:17.428
But I'm so…

44
00:02:21.766 --> 00:02:23.726
Are they still talking?

45
00:02:23.810 --> 00:02:24.894
-Really.
-It's dark now.

46
00:02:24.978 --> 00:02:28.898
-He's more persistent than I thought.
-I think that's his charm.

47
00:02:28.982 --> 00:02:30.108
You know. some couples

48
00:02:30.191 --> 00:02:33.486
talk on the phone
for three hours straight.

49
00:02:34.112 --> 00:02:36.531
-He's good at meeting those needs.
-Yes.

50
00:02:40.743 --> 00:02:43.454
What have you been
talking about for so long?

51
00:02:43.538 --> 00:02:45.748
-Us?
-Are you still not done?

52
00:02:46.332 --> 00:02:47.750
Since it's cold. let's head inside.

53
00:02:48.251 --> 00:02:50.044
-Sure.
-Since it's cold.

54
00:02:51.171 --> 00:02:52.088
Inside. where exactly?

55
00:02:52.589 --> 00:02:54.257
-Let's go to the Cafeteria.
-Okay.

56
00:02:56.092 --> 00:02:57.510
-Here.
-Okay.

57
00:02:58.094 --> 00:02:59.762
-They won't leave her side.
-This is fun.

58
00:02:59.846 --> 00:03:01.931
-This is fun.
-Sung-min won't leave.

59
00:03:02.015 --> 00:03:03.433
-He's not giving them space.
-No.

60
00:03:03.516 --> 00:03:04.934
Isn't it about time he left?

61
00:03:05.018 --> 00:03:06.936
-They've already talked.
-For two hours.

62
00:03:07.020 --> 00:03:08.229
He knows he needs to stay.

63
00:03:08.313 --> 00:03:09.814
-It's already dark.
-Yes.

64
00:03:11.316 --> 00:03:12.400
Sit in the middle.

65
00:03:13.067 --> 00:03:14.319
-Sit in the middle.
-Okay.

66
00:03:16.529 --> 00:03:17.614
This is funny.

67
00:03:17.697 --> 00:03:19.949
What have you been
talking about for so long?

68
00:03:20.033 --> 00:03:21.409
Just this and that.

69
00:03:21.492 --> 00:03:23.202
There's no end.

70
00:03:23.286 --> 00:03:25.413
If you hadn't come.
we'd have talked until dawn.

71
00:03:28.333 --> 00:03:29.250
Just saying.

72
00:03:32.795 --> 00:03:35.590
Wait. did you two go to Paradise before?

73
00:03:35.673 --> 00:03:36.549
-Yes.
-Once.

74
00:03:37.467 --> 00:03:39.302
Who picked who?

75
00:03:39.886 --> 00:03:40.762
We picked each other.

76
00:03:41.262 --> 00:03:42.513
-You guys matched?
-Yes.

77
00:03:42.597 --> 00:03:44.015
We played a game together.

78
00:03:44.098 --> 00:03:45.099
We matched.

79
00:03:46.267 --> 00:03:49.270
We played a game. talked.
and matched with each other.

80
00:03:52.065 --> 00:03:52.899
So we went.

81
00:03:57.028 --> 00:03:59.322
I wonder what will happen tomorrow.

82
00:03:59.405 --> 00:04:00.865
I'm so curious.

83
00:04:01.616 --> 00:04:03.034
I'm really curious.

84
00:04:03.785 --> 00:04:05.161
Is this how it's going to be?

85
00:04:08.539 --> 00:04:10.208
I can't believe what I'm seeing.

86
00:04:10.291 --> 00:04:11.584
It's a true love triangle.

87
00:04:22.470 --> 00:04:23.805
I wonder what we'll do.

88
00:04:26.182 --> 00:04:27.725
Sung-min is just saying whatever.

89
00:04:27.809 --> 00:04:29.269
-He's just guarding her.
-Yes.

90
00:04:29.352 --> 00:04:30.353
-Seems so.
-It's his spot.

91
00:04:30.436 --> 00:04:32.355
-He's just keeping watch.
-Yes.

92
00:04:33.606 --> 00:04:34.941
I wonder what we'll do.

93
00:04:41.614 --> 00:04:43.116
Shall we go eat ice cream?

94
00:04:45.451 --> 00:04:46.369
{\an8}WATER FOUNTAIN

95
00:04:46.452 --> 00:04:49.038
{\an8}<i>-There's ice cream?</i>
<i>-There's ice cream at the water fountain?</i>

96
