00:57:48.339 --> 00:57:50.383
No one can stay in first place forever.

984
00:57:51.176 --> 00:57:52.802
Wow. I-geon.

985
00:58:03.938 --> 00:58:05.190
I-geon really did it.

986
00:58:05.273 --> 00:58:07.859
What if I-geon falls asleep
as soon as he gets to Paradise?

987
00:58:08.485 --> 00:58:11.237
-What?
-He wrung himself dry.

988
00:58:11.821 --> 00:58:12.822
He'll pass out.

989
00:58:12.906 --> 00:58:14.866
He'll eat and lie down for a bit.

990
00:58:14.949 --> 00:58:16.784
-And wake up the next day.
-Yes.

991
00:58:16.868 --> 00:58:18.036
He used all his energy.

992
00:58:18.119 --> 00:58:19.412
-"Good morning."
-"Good morning."

993
00:58:19.496 --> 00:58:22.749
-Gosh. I'm so worried.
-You're so mean.

994
00:58:22.832 --> 00:58:23.833
I'm just worried.

995
00:58:23.917 --> 00:58:26.461
-He's so mean.
-It's their last Paradise trip.

996
00:58:30.715 --> 00:58:31.799
What is it?

997
00:58:31.883 --> 00:58:33.968
-I've got a feeling that Sung-min…
-Yes?

998
00:58:34.052 --> 00:58:36.721
…won't leave Go-eun's side
until the very last second.

999
00:58:37.597 --> 00:58:39.474
-Seriously.
-He won't leave her side.

1000
00:58:39.557 --> 00:58:40.850
-Starting now.
-Really?

1001
00:58:40.934 --> 00:58:42.977
He'll say. "Don't change your mind."

1002
00:58:45.313 --> 00:58:46.356
That's so funny.

1003
00:58:46.981 --> 00:58:49.651
Why are we so tired from just watching?

1004
00:58:49.734 --> 00:58:52.028
-I'm so exhausted.
-Same.

1005
00:58:52.111 --> 00:58:54.197
I'm curious to know who I-geon likes.

1006
00:58:54.280 --> 00:58:57.367
I think I-geon is obviously
interested in Go-eun.

1007
00:58:57.450 --> 00:59:01.162
He kept on trying to talk to Go-eun.

1008
00:59:01.246 --> 00:59:03.206
If not. he wouldn't have tried so hard.

1009
00:59:03.289 --> 00:59:04.624
-Right.
-He's going anyway.

1010
00:59:04.707 --> 00:59:08.127
-On top of that. his opponent…
-It was him.

1011
00:59:08.211 --> 00:59:10.964
-Hyeon-woo?
-I didn't think he'd beat Hyeon-woo.

1012
00:59:11.047 --> 00:59:12.590
How do you feel. Go-eun?

1013
00:59:13.841 --> 00:59:15.760
I feel the same about all of them.

1014
00:59:16.678 --> 00:59:18.638
I think today's trip will be important.

1015
00:59:18.721 --> 00:59:22.475
-Hyeon-woo must be in a dilemma.
-Exactly. who will he go with?

1016
00:59:23.184 --> 00:59:26.062
-Exactly.
-It'll depend on who I-geon picks.

1017
00:59:26.145 --> 00:59:26.980
Yes.

1018
00:59:34.862 --> 00:59:36.197
<i>Singles.</i>

1019
00:59:36.698 --> 00:59:39.576
<i>You are free to go on dates</i>
<i>at your discretion.</i>

1020
00:59:41.661 --> 00:59:42.579
I'll be back.

1021
00:59:42.662 --> 00:59:43.663
This is tough.

1022
00:59:43.746 --> 00:59:45.540
Sung-min is going right away.

1023
00:59:45.623 --> 00:59:47.292
-Gosh.
-You were right.

1024
00:59:47.375 --> 00:59:49.168
-Just like I had predicted.
-Yes.

1025
00:59:49.669 --> 00:59:51.671
He'll be with her until she leaves.

1026
00:59:53.047 --> 00:59:54.299
What is this?

1027
00:59:54.882 --> 00:59:56.217
We're free to go on dates.

1028
00:59:58.011 --> 01:00:00.179
Ha-eun. can you call Go-eun for me?

1029
01:00:00.263 --> 01:00:02.432
-I'm here.
-Are you in the vanity room?

1030
01:00:02.515 --> 01:00:03.641
Gather here. everyone.

1031
01:00:03.725 --> 01:00:07.270
Everyone and anyone
you're looking for is here.

1032
01:00:07.353 --> 01:00:08.313
Come in.

1033
01:00:08.980 --> 01:00:11.149
-Can I talk to Sung-hun?
-Sure.

1034
01:00:11.816 --> 01:00:13.359
Look at Mina Sue.

1035
01:00:13.443 --> 01:00:14.944
Everyone's being so proactive.

1036
01:00:15.945 --> 01:00:18.031
-I'm stressed.
-You're stressed?

1037
01:00:18.114 --> 01:00:20.366
This is the first time
I've felt so stressed out here.

1038
01:00:22.869 --> 01:00:24.704
-I'm annoyed.
-You're annoyed?

1039
01:00:25.288 --> 01:00:27.123
Sung-min will go as far away as possible.

1040
01:00:29.751 --> 01:00:32.003
He'll take her to the other side.

1041
01:00:32.086 --> 01:00:34.130
He'll go to the farthest possible spot.

1042
01:00:37.133 --> 01:00:39.093
What's on your mind?

1043
01:00:40.261 --> 01:00:42.347
I'm feeling quite uneasy.

1044
01:00:43.056 --> 01:00:44.891
-I'm feeling on edge.
-Why?

1045
01:00:44.974 --> 01:00:46.976
Who knows what will happen?

1046
01:00:49.187 --> 01:00:52.523
I really want to know
what's on your mind at the moment.

1047
01:00:53.608 --> 01:00:54.692
-Me?
-Yes.

1048
01:00:54.776 --> 01:00:56.903
I'm not so sure myself.

1049
01:00:56.986 --> 01:00:58.988
-At the moment?
-It's really tough.

1050
01:01:00.156 --> 01:01:01.658
What a fickle woman you are.

1051
01:01:02.158 --> 01:01:04.285
It's because everyone's great.

1052
01:01:04.369 --> 01:01:05.662
They're all so kind.

1053
01:01:06.162 --> 01:01:09.540
I'm just trying to find someone
who's the perfect fit for me.

1054
01:01:10.375 --> 01:01:11.542
-Right.
-Yes.

1055
01:01:13.044 --> 01:01:14.754
You're being taken away again.

1056
01:01:16.255 --> 01:01:17.340
We don't know yet.

1057
01:01:17.924 --> 01:01:19.676
My gut says you are.

1058
01:01:21.844 --> 01:01:23.638
-You're suddenly anxious.
-Yes.

1059
01:01:23.721 --> 01:01:25.932
I know where my heart lies.

1060
01:01:26.557 --> 01:01:29.602
I'm just worried
you might change your mind. Go-eun.

1061
01:01:30.186 --> 01:01:31.479
Of course. I'm anxious.

1062
01:01:32.980 --> 01:01:33.898
Are you worried?

1063
01:01:34.440 --> 01:01:35.358
A little…

1064
01:01:35.441 --> 01:01:36.359
No. a lot.

1065
01:01:36.984 --> 01:01:39.654
You weren't this anxious
when I went with Hyeon-woo.

1066
01:01:39.737 --> 01:01:41.197
-You weren't like this.
-True.

1067
01:01:41.280 --> 01:01:44.575
I didn't feel this way
when you went with Hyeon-woo.

1068
01:01:45.493 --> 01:01:48.162
I don't know why.
but I feel very anxious this time.

1069
01:01:49.580 --> 01:01:52.375
Going to Paradise a second time
could change things.

1070
01:01:52.458 --> 01:01:53.292
That's true.

1071
01:01:55.420 --> 01:01:57.547
Maybe I was too nonchalant until now.

1072
01:01:58.339 --> 01:01:59.382
-You?
-Yes.

1073
01:01:59.465 --> 01:02:00.758
Don't have nice talks.

1074
01:02:01.300 --> 01:02:02.635
No. don't talk at all.

1075
01:02:03.678 --> 01:02:06.180
Just listen to him talk.

1076
01:02:07.306 --> 01:02:08.224
Nothing else.

1077
01:02:13.146 --> 01:02:16.315
-I wonder what Hyeon-woo will do.
-I see.

1078
01:02:16.399 --> 01:02:18.818
If he had won first place.
he'd have probably…

1079
01:02:18.901 --> 01:02:21.320
He and I like the same person.

1080
01:02:21.946 --> 01:02:24.115
I'm curious to know who he'll go with.

1081
01:02:32.707 --> 01:02:37.462
Hyeon-woo must have a lot on his mind
since he's only interested in Go-eun.

1082
01:02:37.545 --> 01:02:42.383
Do you think he'll pick someone
who doesn't have any ties yet?

1083
01:02:42.467 --> 01:02:46.471
Or will he go for his second pick
even if he's barely interested in her?

1084
01:02:46.554 --> 01:02:48.222
-He doesn't have a second pick.
-I agree.

1085
01:02:48.306 --> 01:02:49.515
-You think so?
-Yes.

1086
01:02:49.599 --> 01:02:51.517
-He's devoted.
-He is.

1087
01:02:52.018 --> 01:02:53.644
{\an8}INFERNO

1088
01:02:53.728 --> 01:02:58.316
{\an8}<i>Now. we're going to match the couples</i>
<i>who will go on a date in Paradise.</i>

1089
01:03:02.987 --> 01:03:04.614
-It's decision time.
-It is.

1090
01:03:04.697 --> 01:03:07.366
-I'm curious about Hyeon-woo's pick.
-I see.

1091
01:03:16.501 --> 01:03:17.835
Today will be fun too.

1092
01:03:19.837 --> 01:03:21.839
<i>We'll begin with first-place winner.</i>
<i>Jo I-geon.</i>

1093
01:03:21.923 --> 01:03:26.385
<i>Please choose the person</i>
<i>you'd like to go to Paradise with.</i>

1094
01:03:28.638 --> 01:03:33.893
<i>My only goal from the start</i>
<i>was to win first place no matter what.</i>

1095
01:03:47.907 --> 01:03:50.159
The person I'd like to go
to Paradise with is…

1096
01:03:53.621 --> 01:03:55.039
Kim Go-eun.

1097
01:03:56.874 --> 01:03:59.126
<i>The person Jo I-geon chose is</i>

1098
01:03:59.669 --> 01:04:01.087
<i>Kim Go-eun.</i>

1099
01:04:09.345 --> 01:04:10.596
<i>Kim Go-eun.</i>

1100
01:04:10.680 --> 01:04:13.099
<i>Jo I-geon and Kim Go-eun.</i>

1101
01:04:13.182 --> 01:04:14.308
-See you.
<i>-Please hold hands…</i>

1102
01:04:14.392 --> 01:04:16.185
-What do I do?
<i>-…and leave for Paradise.</i>

1103
01:04:16.686 --> 01:04:19.146
Just enjoy it. My Lady.

1104
01:04:19.230 --> 01:04:20.857
-Have fun.
-See you later.

1105
01:04:20.940 --> 01:04:23.067
You're so popular!

1106
01:04:23.150 --> 01:04:26.821
Come to think of it. I-geon and Go-eun
had ice cream together yesterday.

1107
01:04:29.907 --> 01:04:31.409
I have a gut feeling

1108
01:04:31.492 --> 01:04:32.743
something big is coming.

1109
01:04:32.827 --> 01:04:33.661
Right?

1110
01:04:34.328 --> 01:04:35.288
Things will settle…

1111
01:04:35.371 --> 01:04:36.956
-Case closed.
-…on this Paradise trip.

1112
01:04:47.300 --> 01:04:48.593
<i>It felt strange.</i>

1113
01:04:48.676 --> 01:04:50.511
Maybe it was because
my feelings had changed

1114
01:04:50.595 --> 01:04:52.972
or because it was
our second trip to Paradise.

1115
01:04:53.055 --> 01:04:57.810
but I started to get really nervous
the moment she walked out of her lodging.

1116
01:05:03.316 --> 01:05:04.150
Let's go.

1117
01:05:04.650 --> 01:05:05.568
Let's go.

1118
01:05:06.402 --> 01:05:07.486
Let's go.

1119
01:05:11.073 --> 01:05:12.074
Right in front of him…

1120
01:05:12.575 --> 01:05:13.576
Don't look.

1121
01:05:22.084 --> 01:05:24.629
-They look like newlyweds.
-I know. right?

1122
01:05:24.712 --> 01:05:27.214
-They're both wearing white.
-They are matching.

1123
01:05:28.382 --> 01:05:30.843
-Gosh. my hands are sweaty.
-Why?

1124
01:05:31.802 --> 01:05:33.304
-Are you nervous?
-I guess so.

1125
01:05:34.680 --> 01:05:37.558
-I'm not usually the type to get nervous.
-Really?

1126
01:05:42.605 --> 01:05:45.900
<i>Next is the second-place winner.</i>
<i>Shin Hyeon-woo.</i>

1127
01:05:48.986 --> 01:05:51.030
Who do you think Hyeon-woo will pick?

1128
01:05:51.113 --> 01:05:52.615
-I have no idea.
-No one knows?

1129
01:05:52.698 --> 01:05:55.785
Maybe he'll pick someone new.
like Ye-jin or Ha-eun.

1130
01:05:55.868 --> 01:05:57.203
I'm dying to know.

1131
01:05:57.995 --> 01:05:59.538
Seriously. who will he pick?

1132
01:05:59.622 --> 01:06:02.833
-Ye-jin's the only one with no ties.
-Right.

1133
01:06:03.960 --> 01:06:05.169
Will he pick Mina Sue?

1134
01:06:07.296 --> 01:06:08.339
I'm so curious.

1135
01:06:09.548 --> 01:06:10.424
<i>Shin Hyeon-woo.</i>

1136
01:06:11.050 --> 01:06:15.096
<i>Please choose the person</i>
<i>you'd like to go to Paradise with.</i>

1137
01:06:17.098 --> 01:06:20.226
<i>The person I'd like to go</i>
<i>to Paradise with is Kim Go-eun.</i>

1138
01:06:20.851 --> 01:06:24.021
However. since I-geon won first place.

1139
01:06:24.105 --> 01:06:26.899
I thought long and hard

1140
01:06:26.983 --> 01:06:30.152
<i>about what I should do</i>
<i>if he picked Go-eun.</i>

1141
01:06:32.279 --> 01:06:34.323
<i>The person Shin Hyeon-woo chose is…</i>

1142
01:06:42.331 --> 01:06:45.209
I have decided

1143
01:06:46.377 --> 01:06:47.503
not to go to Paradise.

1144
01:06:49.922 --> 01:06:51.674
-What? Is that allowed?
-Is it?

1145
01:06:51.757 --> 01:06:52.883
-What?
-He can do that?

1146
01:06:52.967 --> 01:06:55.261
-This is the first.
-Yes. it is.

1147
01:06:57.013 --> 01:06:59.140
<i>The person Shin Hyeon-woo chose is…</i>

1148
01:06:59.765 --> 01:07:00.683
<i>no one.</i>

1149
01:07:01.851 --> 01:07:05.813
<i>Shin Hyeon-woo has decided not to go.</i>

1150
01:07:05.896 --> 01:07:07.106
<i>…no one.</i>

1151
01:07:18.993 --> 01:07:23.497
-So you don't have to choose.
-I didn't know that was an option.

1152
01:07:24.457 --> 01:07:29.628
<i>Today. I decided not to pick anyone</i>
<i>to go to Paradise with.</i>

1153
01:07:29.712 --> 01:07:36.010
I had no other option but Go-eun
from the start.

1154
01:07:38.179 --> 01:07:39.847
So I decided not to go.

1155
01:07:41.432 --> 01:07:42.892
-Gosh.
-Even if he doesn't go.

1156
01:07:42.975 --> 01:07:44.393
-she won't be there.
-Right.

1157
01:07:44.477 --> 01:07:46.353
-Gosh. seriously.
-Good for him.

1158
01:07:46.437 --> 01:07:47.897
If Go-eun hears about this…

1159
01:07:47.980 --> 01:07:50.149
-He's so single-minded.
-Really.

1160
01:07:50.232 --> 01:07:52.610
I just got goosebumps everywhere.

1161
01:07:52.693 --> 01:07:54.904
That is wild.

1162
01:07:55.529 --> 01:07:58.532
-Hyeon-woo is so cool.
-He really is cool.

1163
01:07:58.616 --> 01:08:01.327
-What an admirable choice.
-It was totally unexpected.

1164
01:08:02.495 --> 01:08:04.747
<i>He's fallen hard for Go-eun.</i>

1165
01:08:12.046 --> 01:08:15.174
<i>Last is the third-place winner.</i>
<i>Youn Hyun-jae.</i>

1166
01:08:15.758 --> 01:08:16.801
<i>Youn Hyun-jae.</i>

1167
01:08:16.884 --> 01:08:20.805
<i>Please choose the person</i>
<i>you'd like to go to Paradise with.</i>

1168
01:08:22.181 --> 01:08:24.600
The person I'd like to go
to Paradise with is…

1169
01:08:27.186 --> 01:08:28.354
Lee Joo-young.

1170
01:08:33.400 --> 01:08:34.777
-That's right.
-Yes.

1171
01:08:34.860 --> 01:08:35.820
His last chance.

1172
01:08:35.903 --> 01:08:37.988
-It's the best he can do.
-Really.

1173
01:08:38.697 --> 01:08:39.907
<i>Lee Joo-young.</i>

1174
01:08:40.491 --> 01:08:45.162
<i>Youn Hyun-jae and Lee Joo-young.</i>
<i>Please hold hands and leave for Paradise.</i>

1175
01:08:45.246 --> 01:08:46.080
See you later.

1176
01:08:46.163 --> 01:08:47.540
-I'll be back.
-See you.

1177
01:08:48.165 --> 01:08:49.625
<i>Lee Joo-young.</i>

1178
01:09:03.931 --> 01:09:04.974
Hello.

1179
01:09:10.521 --> 01:09:11.397
I'm sorry

1180
01:09:11.981 --> 01:09:13.149
for making you get wet.

1181
01:09:14.692 --> 01:09:15.526
It's raining.

1182
01:09:16.610 --> 01:09:19.530
-Why is it raining all of a sudden?
-I know. right?

1183
01:09:20.656 --> 01:09:21.949
What a new experience.

1184
01:09:22.032 --> 01:09:23.993
-It's raining.
-I won. but it's raining.

1185
01:09:26.829 --> 01:09:31.125
<i>Today's Paradise-bound</i>
<i>couple matching is over.</i>

1186
01:09:36.172 --> 01:09:39.633
I can't believe he didn't choose.
That has never happened before.

1187
01:09:55.149 --> 01:09:56.817
{\an8}Hyeon-woo decided not to go.

1188
01:10:01.447 --> 01:10:03.449
{\an8}Hyeon-woo decided not to go.

1189
01:10:04.033 --> 01:10:06.035
{\an8}-He's not coming.
-I see.

1190
01:10:06.577 --> 01:10:07.453
{\an8}Is that allowed?

1191
01:10:08.412 --> 01:10:09.413
{\an8}It's because of you.

1192
01:10:18.464 --> 01:10:21.842
When I heard Hyeon-woo decided not to go.
I was really shocked.

1193
01:10:21.926 --> 01:10:24.511
It felt like something Hyeon-woo would do.

1194
01:10:25.012 --> 01:10:27.473
I was shocked

1195
01:10:27.556 --> 01:10:30.726
but also touched by Hyeon-woo.

1196
01:10:32.102 --> 01:10:34.897
Hyeon-woo. you were so cool.

1197
01:10:34.980 --> 01:10:36.065
No. it's nothing.

1198
01:10:36.690 --> 01:10:38.651
I'm not cool. I'm feeling bitter.

1199
01:10:39.818 --> 01:10:41.195
I'm extremely disappointed.

1200
01:11:03.592 --> 01:11:05.678
Oh no. Her mind is somewhere else.

1201
01:11:06.345 --> 01:11:08.847
I-geon is experienced. so he's got this.

1202
01:11:09.473 --> 01:11:10.849
-He's got this. right?
-Yes.

1203
01:11:12.017 --> 01:11:14.103
{\an8}PARADISE
JO I-GEON & KIM GO-EUN

1204
01:11:14.186 --> 01:11:16.605
{\an8}-Let's rest for a bit.
-Okay.

1205
01:11:17.982 --> 01:11:19.650
Oh. I have something to do.

1206
01:11:20.234 --> 01:11:21.902
There's something you have to do.

1207
01:11:21.986 --> 01:11:24.613
-What?
-I have something stuck under my nail.

1208
01:11:25.739 --> 01:11:27.700
-Is it sand?
-I think?

1209
01:11:28.534 --> 01:11:30.828
I don't know if it's sand or blood.

1210
01:11:32.121 --> 01:11:33.831
-Can you see it?
-Yes.

1211
01:11:35.332 --> 01:11:36.500
-Does it hurt?
-Yes.

1212
01:11:37.126 --> 01:11:39.044
Is this sand?

1213
01:11:41.797 --> 01:11:44.466
Take it out now. just like that.

1214
01:11:45.175 --> 01:11:47.136
-You can use your fingernail…
-Hang on.

1215
01:11:49.805 --> 01:11:50.764
How do I do this?

1216
01:11:51.682 --> 01:11:53.517
Do I really have to do this for you?

1217
01:11:56.437 --> 01:11:58.564
Wait. I have tweezers.

1218
01:12:06.405 --> 01:12:07.406
Tell me if it hurts.

1219
01:12:08.157 --> 01:12:09.575
-Is it sand?
-Yes.

1220
01:12:09.658 --> 01:12:10.784
What about this black thing?

1221
01:12:10.868 --> 01:12:13.162
Wait. I'll try to poke it and check first.

1222
01:12:15.998 --> 01:12:16.915
It hurts to touch.

1223
01:12:16.999 --> 01:12:18.584
-It does?
-I'll just leave it.

1224
01:12:19.543 --> 01:12:22.629
-Nice.
-What's "nice"?

1225
01:12:23.839 --> 01:12:25.299
What exactly is nice?

1226
01:12:28.135 --> 01:12:30.512
-I have a question.
-Okay.

1227
01:12:30.596 --> 01:12:33.182
If you hadn't won first place
and had to pick someone else.

1228
01:12:33.265 --> 01:12:34.308
who would you have chosen?

1229
01:12:35.976 --> 01:12:38.729
There's really no one else.
so I'm not sure.

1230
01:12:39.897 --> 01:12:40.731
Maybe Ha-eun.

1231
01:12:40.814 --> 01:12:43.067
But Ha-eun likes Jae-jin.

1232
01:12:45.235 --> 01:12:46.945
There's something
I've been meaning to say.

1233
01:12:49.573 --> 01:12:50.866
The two of us…

1234
01:12:50.949 --> 01:12:55.454
We could've gotten closer
if we wanted to. right?

1235
01:12:56.038 --> 01:12:58.248
I may have said otherwise.

1236
01:12:58.332 --> 01:13:03.379
but subconsciously. I wonder
how well we know each other.

1237
01:13:04.046 --> 01:13:05.089
Right? It's true.

1238
01:13:05.172 --> 01:13:08.133
-I just thought it was a shame.
-Right.

1239
01:13:08.217 --> 01:13:10.177
I think because of that…

1240
01:13:10.260 --> 01:13:12.846
I also felt that way at first.
That's why I acted the way I did.

1241
01:13:12.930 --> 01:13:14.598
The same goes for me.

1242
01:13:14.681 --> 01:13:16.266
It's stuff like that.

1243
01:13:16.975 --> 01:13:21.563
I think that's why I initially
made things confusing between us.

1244
01:13:21.647 --> 01:13:23.399
-You know what I mean?
-Yes. I know.

1245
01:13:23.482 --> 01:13:26.443
After we talked for the first time

1246
01:13:26.527 --> 01:13:29.613
and realized we knew each other.

1247
01:13:29.696 --> 01:13:32.783
I wondered if I should've said

1248
01:13:33.367 --> 01:13:35.911
we could keep talking anyway.

1249
01:13:35.994 --> 01:13:36.829
I see.

1250
01:13:43.460 --> 01:13:45.295
You were impressive during the game.

1251
01:13:47.464 --> 01:13:49.842
-Who's the strongest now?
-It's you now.

1252
01:13:49.925 --> 01:13:53.011
-I'm the strongest now.
-Yes. Jo I-geon is the strongest.

1253
01:13:53.637 --> 01:13:56.890
-Did you cheer for me?
-No.

1254
01:13:56.974 --> 01:13:58.100
-Not at all.
-Why not?

1255
01:13:58.183 --> 01:14:00.561
You wouldn't have chosen me
if you had gone to Paradise.

1256
01:14:02.062 --> 01:14:03.439
I already knew that.

1257
01:14:03.522 --> 01:14:05.441
-What?
-I hoped you'd lose.

1258
01:14:05.524 --> 01:14:06.817
-Really?
-Yes.

1259
01:14:08.193 --> 01:14:09.611
Do you see this? I got hurt.

1260
01:14:10.362 --> 01:14:12.489
Why? From the game?

1261
01:14:12.573 --> 01:14:14.700
Yes. a cat named Hee-sun scratched me.

1262
01:14:16.577 --> 01:14:20.873
-Hee-sun was very cool.
-What about me?

1263
01:14:22.749 --> 01:14:24.877
You were kind of…

1264
01:14:25.586 --> 01:14:27.921
-Wasn't I cool?
-Hee-sun was beyond comparison.

1265
01:14:28.005 --> 01:14:31.258
-Really?
-She even had a fierce look on her face.

1266
01:14:31.341 --> 01:14:32.301
Seriously.

1267
01:14:32.384 --> 01:14:35.304
-You should've talked with Hee-sun then.
-I wanted to.

1268
01:14:36.013 --> 01:14:37.181
What's wrong with you?

1269
01:14:37.890 --> 01:14:39.808
What's your problem?

1270
01:14:40.601 --> 01:14:42.394
You lose 50 points.

1271
01:14:44.813 --> 01:14:45.772
Seriously.

1272
01:14:46.440 --> 01:14:47.357
I want to leave.

1273
01:14:49.485 --> 01:14:51.653
You're one to talk.

1274
01:14:52.446 --> 01:14:53.947
-You're so funny.
-I'm leaving.

1275
01:14:54.031 --> 01:14:56.366
-Look who's talking.
-I want to leave.

1276
01:14:56.450 --> 01:14:59.036
-Stay here alone.
-You went on a walk today. too.

1277
01:14:59.119 --> 01:15:00.454
Hey. seriously…

1278
01:15:01.955 --> 01:15:03.373
-I'm busy!
-Seriously…

1279
01:15:03.457 --> 01:15:05.792
I'm busy. so hurry up and ask me out.

1280
01:15:05.876 --> 01:15:08.921
I was so dumbfounded
when I saw you on that walk today.

1281
01:15:09.588 --> 01:15:10.839
Why can't you just sleep?

1282
01:15:10.923 --> 01:15:12.758
-I wanted to!
-What were you doing up?

1283
01:15:12.841 --> 01:15:14.176
I mean. seriously.

1284
01:15:16.678 --> 01:15:18.805
I'll take a walk with you here tomorrow.

1285
01:15:19.973 --> 01:15:21.141
No. I'm going to sleep.

1286
01:15:22.851 --> 01:15:24.353
Let's take a walk around here.

1287
01:15:24.436 --> 01:15:25.979
A walk around the pool.

1288
01:15:27.773 --> 01:15:28.941
A morning swim.

1289
01:15:29.608 --> 01:15:30.442
All right.

1290
01:15:31.026 --> 01:15:32.277
"All right"?

1291
01:15:32.945 --> 01:15:36.114
-Were you joking?
-I can't believe you said. "All right."

1292
01:15:38.200 --> 01:15:41.161
We can't swim first thing in the morning.

1293
01:15:42.329 --> 01:15:43.205
You're so odd.

1294
01:15:46.667 --> 01:15:48.001
Do you get jealous?

1295
01:15:51.380 --> 01:15:53.006
I get very jealous.

1296
01:15:53.090 --> 01:15:54.091
Very jealous?

1297
01:15:55.717 --> 01:15:57.928
When I like someone.

1298
01:15:58.554 --> 01:16:01.390
it's hard to control myself.

1299
01:16:02.266 --> 01:16:03.100
Sometimes

1300
01:16:03.684 --> 01:16:04.810
it's scary.

1301
01:16:05.435 --> 01:16:10.399
Because it's hard to go about my life
when I can't control my emotions.

1302
01:16:10.482 --> 01:16:12.776
You must fall head over heels for them.

1303
01:16:12.859 --> 01:16:16.029
Yes. I just find everything
about them adorable.

1304
01:16:18.824 --> 01:16:21.827
-Do you get jealous?
-I get jealous a lot.

1305
01:16:22.327 --> 01:16:23.495
-A lot?
-Yes.

1306
01:16:24.496 --> 01:16:27.082
-You don't look like it.
-I know.

1307
01:16:27.624 --> 01:16:29.376
-I get that a lot.
-I bet.

1308
01:16:31.211 --> 01:16:32.921
Is it pouring or drizzling?

1309
01:16:33.714 --> 01:16:36.300
It's starting to pour.

1310
01:16:43.223 --> 01:16:44.933
Can you open the curtain a little more?

1311
01:16:48.145 --> 01:16:49.396
It's already fully open.

1312
01:16:50.564 --> 01:16:52.983
-I meant--
-How can I open it any further?

1313
01:16:56.403 --> 01:16:57.779
He's right.

1314
01:17:02.576 --> 01:17:03.827
How can I open it any further?

1315
01:17:03.910 --> 01:17:07.205
I want a better view
of the rain falling on the pool.

1316
01:17:09.082 --> 01:17:11.168
You act like you won't.
but you do it anyway.

1317
01:17:14.129 --> 01:17:15.005
-Like this?
-Yes.

1318
01:17:15.088 --> 01:17:17.174
Oh. that's perfect.

1319
01:17:17.841 --> 01:17:19.343
-But it's fully opened.
-Gosh.

1320
01:17:19.885 --> 01:17:21.511
I like I-geon's response.

1321
01:17:21.595 --> 01:17:23.388
-He ends up doing it anyway.
-Right.

1322
01:17:23.472 --> 01:17:25.557
-He grumbles.
-He does it while grumbling.

1323
01:17:27.517 --> 01:17:28.477
That's so funny.

1324
01:17:29.394 --> 01:17:31.730
Can you see the rain from where you are?

1325
01:17:32.522 --> 01:17:33.357
Yes.

1326
01:17:45.661 --> 01:17:49.414
-This is so relaxing.
-Yes.

1327
01:17:50.666 --> 01:17:53.251
I don't think
I'll ever forget this moment.

1328
01:17:55.921 --> 01:17:58.090
-I-geon is for sure charming.
-He is.

1329
01:17:58.173 --> 01:17:59.007
He really is.

1330
01:17:59.091 --> 01:18:01.677
He doesn't go in the direction
you want him to.

1331
01:18:02.260 --> 01:18:04.930
but he still has a serious side.

1332
01:18:05.013 --> 01:18:06.765
-He does things for you.
-And he's playful.

1333
01:18:07.432 --> 01:18:09.393
He has such a charming personality.

1334
01:18:09.476 --> 01:18:10.852
The chemistry is different.

1335
01:18:10.936 --> 01:18:13.146
Go-eun and Sung-min seem like friends.

1336
01:18:13.230 --> 01:18:15.440
But with I-geon. they look like a couple.

1337
01:18:15.524 --> 01:18:17.401
But I think we're biased.

1338
01:18:17.484 --> 01:18:19.736
Go-eun is happy with Sung-min.

1339
01:18:19.820 --> 01:18:23.657
but all of us have a tendency
to pair her up with I-geon.

1340
01:18:23.740 --> 01:18:26.284
-Are we?
-Are we the ones who like I-geon?

1341
01:18:26.368 --> 01:18:28.537
To be honest…

1342
01:18:28.620 --> 01:18:32.332
How Go-eun acts with I-geon
and Sung-min is totally different.

1343
01:18:32.416 --> 01:18:34.000
-It's noticeable.
-Really?

1344
01:18:34.084 --> 01:18:37.838
Go-eun's energy is noticeably different.

1345
01:18:37.921 --> 01:18:40.924
I-geon might make mischievous jokes.

1346
01:18:41.007 --> 01:18:44.052
-But Go-eun rolls with it so well.
-She enjoys it.

1347
01:18:44.136 --> 01:18:45.762
-It's fun.
-They have fun together.

1348
01:18:45.846 --> 01:18:47.264
-They're like a couple.
-Yes.

1349
01:18:58.191 --> 01:19:00.694
Who did you come here with again?

1350
01:19:03.113 --> 01:19:05.574
-Let's focus on the positive.
-I'm just curious.

1351
01:19:05.657 --> 01:19:08.118
-I came here with Sung-min.
-Oh. that punk?

1352
01:19:15.333 --> 01:19:17.836
-He's older. so he can say that.
-He's so charming.

1353
01:19:17.919 --> 01:19:21.339
He was hesitant at first.
but now he's expressing himself.

1354
01:19:21.423 --> 01:19:22.424
I find him charming.

1355
01:19:22.507 --> 01:19:23.842
-It's I-geon's charm.
-He's funny.

1356
01:19:23.925 --> 01:19:24.760
He really is.

1357
01:19:34.603 --> 01:19:36.688
-Is it cold?
-No.

1358
01:19:40.817 --> 01:19:42.903
It is a little cold.

1359
01:19:46.907 --> 01:19:48.492
The water is cool here.

1360
01:19:55.874 --> 01:19:57.125
Are you good at swimming?

1361
01:19:58.919 --> 01:20:01.546
-I learned in elementary school.
-Yeah?

1362
01:20:01.630 --> 01:20:04.090
And my body still remembers it.

1363
01:20:04.174 --> 01:20:05.091
-Really?
-Yes.

1364
01:20:05.759 --> 01:20:07.010
I'm not good at swimming.

1365
01:20:07.719 --> 01:20:08.637
Do you know how?

1366
01:20:09.971 --> 01:20:11.139
Why are you over there?

1367
01:20:13.225 --> 01:20:14.184
I'm not good.

1368
01:20:16.228 --> 01:20:17.604
-Want me to teach you?
-Yes.

1369
01:20:17.687 --> 01:20:18.730
It's easy.

1370
01:20:18.814 --> 01:20:19.773
Give me your hands.

1371
01:20:21.441 --> 01:20:22.275
Raise your legs.

1372
01:20:23.360 --> 01:20:24.611
-My legs?
-Hold on tight.

1373
01:20:24.694 --> 01:20:25.821
Hold on.

1374
01:20:25.904 --> 01:20:28.990
-I have to hold on tight?
-Yes. at first.

1375
01:20:30.283 --> 01:20:31.117
Wait…

1376
01:20:31.701 --> 01:20:32.702
Is this it?

1377
01:20:34.037 --> 01:20:36.498
Can't you kick a bit harder?

1378
01:20:38.333 --> 01:20:40.252
Your body has to form a straight line.

1379
01:20:47.092 --> 01:20:49.135
You're not that good. either.

1380
01:20:51.263 --> 01:20:53.014
I don't think I'm doing it right.

1381
01:20:54.224 --> 01:20:55.308
My legs won't float.

1382
01:21:01.523 --> 01:21:02.399
This is funny.

1383
01:21:07.988 --> 01:21:09.823
Does a woman's height matter to you?

1384
01:21:10.365 --> 01:21:11.533
-Height?
-Yes.

1385
01:21:11.616 --> 01:21:14.244
-No. I focus on the overall balance.
-I see.

1386
01:21:14.327 --> 01:21:18.957
-Doesn't that make height important?
-No. it has nothing to do with height.

1387
01:21:20.083 --> 01:21:24.713
If a woman is short.
she looks like a fairy.

1388
01:21:24.796 --> 01:21:26.923
-Yes.
-If she's tall. she looks like a goddess.

1389
01:21:29.384 --> 01:21:31.052
If a man is short. he's annoying.

1390
01:21:31.928 --> 01:21:33.597
If he's tall. he's even more so.

1391
01:21:34.097 --> 01:21:35.223
Everyone but me is annoying.

1392
01:21:36.808 --> 01:21:40.020
-Especially Hyeon-woo and Sung-min.
-Why?

1393
01:21:47.110 --> 01:21:48.069
Are you jealous?

1394
01:21:48.904 --> 01:21:50.405
-What?
-Are you jealous?

1395
01:21:51.281 --> 01:21:53.116
-Does it bother you?
-Yes.

1396
01:21:57.787 --> 01:21:58.955
I won the game today

1397
01:22:00.248 --> 01:22:02.792
because I couldn't stand
the thought of you going to Paradise

1398
01:22:04.085 --> 01:22:05.545
with someone else.

1399
01:22:12.802 --> 01:22:14.387
That was my biggest motivation.

1400
01:22:17.098 --> 01:22:19.267
-Thank goodness I'm here with you.
-Yes.

1401
01:22:27.692 --> 01:22:28.777
You're very handsome.

1402
01:22:31.071 --> 01:22:32.030
You're pretty.

1403
01:22:35.742 --> 01:22:36.743
Are you feeling shy?

1404
01:22:37.661 --> 01:22:39.579
I'm just amazed by your beauty again.

1405
01:22:43.750 --> 01:22:46.127
My left side is prettier.
Look at me from here.

1406
01:22:48.546 --> 01:22:50.131
What if I keep going back and forth?

1407
01:22:50.215 --> 01:22:51.841
-I'll turn.
-You'll keep turning?

1408
01:22:53.510 --> 01:22:55.095
There's no difference.

1409
01:22:55.178 --> 01:22:56.471
-Really?
-Yes.

1410
01:23:12.195 --> 01:23:14.572
Yes. Go-eun likes men like that.

1411
01:23:14.656 --> 01:23:17.617
The way he looks at Go-eun is so sweet.

1412
01:23:17.701 --> 01:23:19.285
-It's like he'll eat her alive.
-What?

1413
01:23:19.369 --> 01:23:21.454
-Like he'll eat her alive.
-Eat her alive?

1414
01:23:33.883 --> 01:23:34.759
Your face

1415
01:23:35.927 --> 01:23:36.970
is really cute too.

1416
01:23:37.595 --> 01:23:38.471
Really?

1417
01:23:40.265 --> 01:23:43.101
-You have cute moments.
-Cute moments? Like when?

1418
01:23:43.643 --> 01:23:45.979
-What?
-When am I cute? I need details.

1419
01:23:49.691 --> 01:23:51.943
Well…

1420
01:23:56.698 --> 01:23:57.615
No.

1421
01:23:59.325 --> 01:24:01.327
How frustrating.

1422
01:24:06.249 --> 01:24:09.335
You don't seem like the jealous type.

1423
01:24:09.419 --> 01:24:12.255
Except when I'm talking
to Sung-min from time to time.

1424
01:24:12.338 --> 01:24:13.298
Right.

1425
01:24:15.550 --> 01:24:17.135
I kind of…

1426
01:24:18.928 --> 01:24:21.890
I try my best not to show it.

1427
01:24:23.433 --> 01:24:24.976
But for some reason today.

1428
01:24:25.060 --> 01:24:28.438
I couldn't stand seeing you
take that walk with him.

1429
01:24:28.521 --> 01:24:29.731
-Really?
-Yes.

1430
01:24:32.817 --> 01:24:35.570
-That's how I felt.
-I didn't know you were working out.

1431
01:24:36.821 --> 01:24:38.573
You didn't even say hello.

1432
01:24:40.241 --> 01:24:41.159
Didn't I?

1433
01:24:58.009 --> 01:25:01.012
That is very cool.

1434
01:25:01.096 --> 01:25:03.139
-What is?
-The scratch you have here.

1435
01:25:08.812 --> 01:25:10.271
I guess you have a cat too.

1436
01:25:11.940 --> 01:25:12.982
It was Sung-min.

1437
01:25:27.705 --> 01:25:28.790
What's on your mind?

1438
01:25:29.958 --> 01:25:31.459
Whether I should go or not.

1439
01:25:37.090 --> 01:25:37.924
Why do you ask?

1440
01:25:50.145 --> 01:25:51.187
What's on your mind?

1441
01:25:53.064 --> 01:25:54.482
Whether you'll come or not.

1442
01:26:13.084 --> 01:26:14.127
You should come.

1443
01:26:22.010 --> 01:26:23.261
I'll go around.

1444
01:26:58.379 --> 01:27:00.506
Do we have a big age gap?

1445
01:27:02.467 --> 01:27:03.301
What?

1446
01:27:03.885 --> 01:27:06.512
Do we have a big age gap?

1447
01:27:08.139 --> 01:27:09.432
I don't know.

1448
01:27:09.515 --> 01:27:10.600
I mean.

1449
01:27:11.559 --> 01:27:13.937
if it doesn't feel that way.
then it probably isn't.

1450
01:27:14.020 --> 01:27:14.854
Right.

1451
01:27:42.924 --> 01:27:43.841
What?

1452
01:27:45.426 --> 01:27:46.469
Why are you smiling?

1453
01:27:50.181 --> 01:27:51.599
You're great.

1454
01:27:52.892 --> 01:27:54.143
I think you're great.

1455
01:28:05.863 --> 01:28:07.991
There isn't a lot of physical contact.

1456
01:28:08.074 --> 01:28:10.535
-but they're so sexy together.
-Yes.

1457
01:28:10.618 --> 01:28:14.372
I think that was the best
pool scene of the season.

1458
01:28:14.455 --> 01:28:15.873
-Right.
-These two.

1459
01:28:16.416 --> 01:28:19.627
Earlier. they were like
"Come or go." or whatever.

1460
01:28:19.711 --> 01:28:22.547
-What are you saying?
-"Or whatever." Don't say it like that.

1461
01:28:22.630 --> 01:28:24.299
It was. "Should I go or not?"

1462
01:28:24.382 --> 01:28:26.676
-I can't even imitate it.
-It was the way he stood. too.

1463
01:28:26.759 --> 01:28:29.012
-Yes. like that.
-He was like this.

1464
01:28:29.095 --> 01:28:31.097
-"Whether you'll come or not."
-Right.

1465
01:28:31.597 --> 01:28:32.765
On opposite ends of the pool.

1466
01:28:32.849 --> 01:28:37.729
It was like a standoff
between a god and a goddess.

1467
01:28:37.812 --> 01:28:40.773
When she said. "You should come."
he said. "I'll go around."

1468
01:28:41.566 --> 01:28:43.818
I think Go-eun's heart
is leaning towards him.

1469
01:28:43.901 --> 01:28:48.114
But I think when she sees
that rougher side of I-geon.

1470
01:28:48.197 --> 01:28:50.825
she thinks they're not compatible.

1471
01:28:50.908 --> 01:28:53.536
but she's drawn to him anyway.

1472
01:28:53.619 --> 01:28:58.499
Sung-min and Hyeon-woo made her feel
at ease and whispered sweet nothings.

1473
01:28:58.583 --> 01:29:00.418
But there's a certain energy with I-geon.

1474
01:29:00.501 --> 01:29:01.878
-Yes.
-There's tension.

1475
01:29:01.961 --> 01:29:04.464
I think that's why I enjoy watching them.

1476
01:29:05.340 --> 01:29:06.341
Did you enjoy it?

1477
01:29:06.424 --> 01:29:09.802
I'm on the edge of my seat
while watching them.

1478
01:29:09.886 --> 01:29:11.512
-Yes.
-"You're great."

1479
01:29:13.097 --> 01:29:14.932
-Shall we take a photo?
-Sure.

1480
01:29:18.311 --> 01:29:19.228
One moment.

1481
01:29:32.450 --> 01:29:33.368
One moment.

1482
01:29:42.377 --> 01:29:43.836
Your eyebrows twitched.

1483
01:29:44.712 --> 01:29:46.089
I was just copying you.

1484
01:29:46.172 --> 01:29:47.131
-Really?
-Yes.

1485
01:29:48.549 --> 01:29:49.675
Oh gosh.

1486
01:29:51.761 --> 01:29:55.139
-I'll take that one.
-I bet it'll look so funny.

1487
01:29:58.351 --> 01:29:59.560
I'll look forward to it.

1488
01:30:12.073 --> 01:30:12.990
Wait.

1489
01:30:19.205 --> 01:30:21.541
I look soulless.
Do I really look like this?

1490
01:30:21.624 --> 01:30:22.875
-No.
-Do I?

1491
01:30:22.959 --> 01:30:25.378
-No. you don't.
-I look silly.

1492
01:30:31.092 --> 01:30:32.009
This is nice.

1493
01:30:35.721 --> 01:30:37.390
When do you want to get married?

1494
01:30:39.267 --> 01:30:40.393
At 28 or 29.

1495
01:30:42.937 --> 01:30:45.648
-What? That's not that far away.
-I know.

1496
01:30:46.732 --> 01:30:49.402
-Isn't that in two or three years?
-Yes.

1497
01:30:50.987 --> 01:30:52.738
I don't think I can become rich by then.

1498
01:30:59.495 --> 01:31:01.205
He's so bold.

1499
01:31:02.582 --> 01:31:04.292
I don't think I can become rich by then.

1500
01:31:08.171 --> 01:31:11.382
-I'll need at least five years.
-I'll be the breadwinner.

1501
01:31:11.924 --> 01:31:13.718
-I make enough.
-That sounds nice.

1502
01:31:17.096 --> 01:31:20.474
-Do you like hypothetical scenarios?
-Yes. give me one.

1503
01:31:20.558 --> 01:31:22.185
-Let's say we're dating.
-Okay.

1504
01:31:22.268 --> 01:31:24.604
What would we fight the most about?

1505
01:31:24.687 --> 01:31:28.024
I feel like we'd fight a few times
because of the way you talk.

1506
01:31:28.608 --> 01:31:30.818
-I think so too.
-Yes.

1507
01:31:31.903 --> 01:31:33.946
But I think I'd fix it right away.

1508
01:31:34.614 --> 01:31:35.489
Right.

1509
01:31:36.115 --> 01:31:37.074
If you mention it.

1510
01:31:38.659 --> 01:31:40.578
What a mesmerizing conversation.

1511
01:31:41.829 --> 01:31:45.124
They keep discussing
their future together.

1512
01:31:45.208 --> 01:31:47.752
-Yes.
-Is this the last stage?

1513
01:31:47.835 --> 01:31:50.087
Where they check
if they're potential partner material?

1514
01:31:50.171 --> 01:31:51.088
It seems like it.

1515
01:31:52.089 --> 01:31:53.007
I think

1516
01:31:54.383 --> 01:31:57.720
I get angry easily.
but I'm also forgetful.

1517
01:32:00.723 --> 01:32:01.724
Yes.

1518
01:32:05.478 --> 01:32:06.312
What?

1519
01:32:06.979 --> 01:32:08.189
Did I sound silly again?

1520
01:32:09.190 --> 01:32:12.276
No. I just thought you were cute.

1521
01:32:13.653 --> 01:32:14.862
not silly.

1522
01:32:15.446 --> 01:32:17.782
Hypothetically. if you made me angry.

1523
01:32:18.616 --> 01:32:22.954
would you give me space
until the next day or…

1524
01:32:23.537 --> 01:32:25.206
I'd probably forget about it by then.

1525
01:32:25.915 --> 01:32:27.917
-If we're dating. you mean?
-Yes.

1526
01:32:28.000 --> 01:32:32.588
-Hypothetically. if we're dating?
-Yes. Assuming it's nothing serious.

1527
01:32:32.672 --> 01:32:35.925
Hypothetically. if we're dating
and you made me angry…

1528
01:32:38.010 --> 01:32:39.679
It would be over with a hug.

1529
01:32:40.179 --> 01:32:41.555
-Really?
-Yes.

1530
01:32:42.181 --> 01:32:43.933
-Easy. right?
-Yes.

1531
01:32:59.573 --> 01:33:00.866
Don't tell anyone else.

1532
01:33:00.950 --> 01:33:02.410
They slept in the same bed.

1533
01:33:02.493 --> 01:33:03.411
What?

1534
01:33:03.494 --> 01:33:04.996
NEXT EPISODE

1535
01:33:07.039 --> 01:33:07.999
Come on. Seung-il.

1536
01:33:08.082 --> 01:33:10.209
You're so charming and attractive.

1537
01:33:13.296 --> 01:33:15.965
What did you just talk about with Hee-sun?

1538
01:33:16.048 --> 01:33:18.801
I really want to be genuine.

1539
01:33:18.884 --> 01:33:20.386
I think she's just leading him on.

1540
01:33:20.469 --> 01:33:22.138
I got goosebumps.

1541
01:33:22.221 --> 01:33:26.183
-Why didn't you pick anyone yesterday?
-I'm only interested in you.

1542
01:33:26.809 --> 01:33:29.103
I'm not going anywhere.

1543
01:33:29.186 --> 01:33:31.605
I'll just be waiting patiently.

1544
01:33:32.648 --> 01:33:34.859
Seeing the two of you talk…

1545
01:33:34.942 --> 01:33:36.527
I shouldn't have let my guard down.

1546
01:33:36.610 --> 01:33:38.696
I think I need to hear you say it.

1547
01:33:39.405 --> 01:33:43.242
<i>We will now begin the final matching.</i>

1548
01:33:43.326 --> 01:33:45.619
<i>The person I'd like</i>
<i>to leave Inferno with is…</i>

1549
01:33:49.540 --> 01:33:52.209
The person I'd like
to leave Inferno with is…

1550
01:33:52.835 --> 01:33:53.794
What?

1551
01:33:54.879 --> 01:33:56.964
None of us saw that coming.

1552
01:33:57.048 --> 01:33:58.883
This is the first time
we've all been wrong.

1553
01:34:30.915 --> 01:34:32.917
Subtitle translation by: Eunice Kim

1554
